202class JSVisitor : public cppgc::Visitor {
203 public:
204 explicit JSVisitor(cppgc::Visitor::Key key) : cppgc::Visitor(key) {}
205 ~JSVisitor() override = default;
206
207 void Trace(const TracedReferenceBase& ref) {
208 if (ref.IsEmptyThreadSafe()) return;
209 Visit(ref);
210 }
211
212 protected:
213 using cppgc::Visitor::Visit;
214
215 virtual void Visit(const TracedReferenceBase& ref) {}
216};

242template <typename T>
243struct TraceTrait<v8::TracedReference<T>> {
244 static cppgc::TraceDescriptor GetTraceDescriptor(const void* self) {
245 return {nullptr, Trace};
246 }
247
248 static void Trace(Visitor* visitor, const void* self) {
249 static_cast<v8::JSVisitor*>(visitor)->Trace(
250 *static_cast<const v8::TracedReference<T>*>(self));
251 }
252};
